==========================================================
  Requirments:
==========================================================
    java:       1.6.x
    maven:  >=  3.0.2


==========================================================
  Status:
==========================================================
    Quicksort is implemented in java, scala and jruby


==========================================================
  How to run:
==========================================================

    # before you need to install my fork version of
    # jruby-maven-plugin:
    git clone git://github.com/rakk/jruby-maven-plugins.git
    cd jruby-maven-plugins
    mvn clean install # it takes a while :(   

    cd ..

    git clone git://github.com/rakk/scalavsjruby.git
    cd scalavsjruby
    mvn clean install # it takes a while :(

    # turn off all java processes...
    ./run.sh

